item.title: Fantasy Look
item.description:
Fantasy Look
This is a makeup look inspired by a romantic fantasy of mine. Normally Im not the type of girl that would create looks based on everyday inspirations but I somehow really wanted to do this one. I guess I was in a romantic mood? Yes, I guess I am a hopeless romantic tehehe.... The romantic fantasy: On a beautiful night, to lie under a starry sky with lots of stars on a grassy hill and chat all night long with him hehe....... So of course, my eyes will symbolise the starry mysterious sky and grass fields. The flexes used will symbolise the stars. Blues and Greens arent normally everyday colours so I used them lightly. Despite using them lightly, this look is still more of a look for night time. The pastel colours are gentle which means your eyes will look Fresh, breezy and cool. So if you are feeling in touch with Nature (lol) I guess you can try out this look or share my fantasy with me hehe. Im sorry if Im slower with videos these days guys.
